    dc:creator "Berning, Björn; Spencer Jones, Mary E.; Vieira, Leandro M." ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the European species of the genus Hincksina Norman, 1903 (Bryozoa, Cheilostomatida, Flustridae)" ;
